sets.subTitle: Centr Power in Gym: Advanced week 3

workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
We're back to get the muscles in your back working overtime. You know this workout packs high reps, so tempo and rest periods are key. Work hard, refresh, then hit it again.


Don't move on until you've nailed your form with the tutorial.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Pull-up and fire up with Bobby so you're ready to hit the racks.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: Prepare to pack the muscle into your lats.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: The wide grip puts the focus on your upper back.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: While your biceps pump, all the major muscles in your back are working hard.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Target your traps for size and power.
